Squid

squid.Rmd
## Linking to GEOS 3.9.3, GDAL 3.5.2, PROJ 8.2.1; sf_use_s2() is TRUE

Squid pose a data problem since they are caught primarily with the same gear as the NE groundfish. A method is required to identify squid trips and to separate these trips from the groundfish trips. Failure to do so will potentially skew the footprint and the effort for the NE groundfish fleet.

Difference between groundfish and squid fishers

  • squid fishers use a smaller mesh net

How much squid landed in each trip?

Fishing footprint of squid trips

Squid trips selected by the percentage of squid landings in each trip

Landings by port

Uses 30% of landings as a squid trip definition
